om/2016/12/21/disclosing-the-primary-email-address-for-each-facebook-user/) , Twitter paid $1,120 for #154963 that could disclose users private emails through clickjacking (a lot of user interaction).\n\nI respect your decision of course, just a little bit disappointed about the bounty amount.\nThanks!","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-02-24T09:52:36.847Z","updated_at":"2017-02-24T09:52:36.847Z","actor":{"username":"zombiehelp54","cleared":true,"url":"/zombiehelp54","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/036/135/f45785bb8d3f76465ddf981069b5b7f94ad1d93c_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1504092,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"After discussion internally, we believe our initial bounty amount is fair based on how we generally award issues and based on the severity of this particular vulnerability.\n\nI'm more than happy to send you some H1 swag, however!","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-02-24T18:47:38.325Z","updated_at":"2017-02-24T18:47:38.325Z","actor":{"username":"reed","cleared":false,"url":"/reed","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/003/132/66d7eadcea16b878bb67bfd697b9542250a801a7_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"security","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1504093,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::SwagAwarded","message":"","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-02-24T18:47:53.268Z","updated_at":"2017-02-24T18:47:53.268Z","actor":{"url":"/security","ibb":